node.text:
Alex Sanchez lives in Warrenville, Illinois, and makes $360,000 a year. While Alex is generally mindful of his spending, his business expenses add up. 

For one week, Alex tracked his spending to see where his money went.

Full interview: https://cnb.cx/2WnnaXU

node.title: What a 26-year-old making $360,000 a year spends in a week

node.text:
After being laid off from his corporate job during the pandemic, @therealchefoh decided to pursue his passion of cooking full-time. He now does around 4 parties per week and makes up to $14,000 per month.

Here's his story.

node.text:
While pursuing his dreams, 'Bling Empire's Kevin Kreider says he racked up as much as $26,000 in credit card debt. 

Luckily, the frugal star adjusted his lifestyle so he could have a fresh start in Los Angeles. Here's how he did it.

node.title: How 'Bling Empire's Kevin Kreider paid off $26,000 in debt

node.text:
40-year-old earning $75,000 a year in LA: ‘I don’t have it all together’ and that’s OK.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CNBC Make It on August 07, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, eyeglasses and text that says 'How 20-year-old 'MkL'' went from poverty to top gamer with nearly half a million dollars in the bank #make'.

node.text:
Leonardo "MkLeo" Lopez Perez, 20, is one of the esports industry's top gamers, widely considered to be the world's best player of "Super Smash Bros." 🎮⁠
⁠
But, growing up, Perez's family didn't have a lot of money. "I remember that we used to sell a lot of things just to have money to eat, like [once] a week," he said. ⁠
⁠
Read how playing video games changed his life at the link in our bio.

node.text:
Each and every little thing you say during a job interview shapes whether or not a hiring manager thinks you are a strong fit for the job. 😅⁠
⁠
At the link in our bio, we're sharing 6 responses to avoid if you want to boost your chances of landing an offer, along with tips and examples of what to say instead. ✅

node.text:
On Friday, Allyson Felix took bronze in the 400m for her 10th Olympic medal. 🥉 ⁠
⁠
She's now tied for the most track and field medals among any American athlete. 👏

node.text:
🚨One-minute money hack🚨
 
Your emergency fund could earn 8 times as much interest in a high-yield savings account. 💸

The average savings account earns an annual percentage yield of around 0.06%, while high-yield accounts currently earn around 0.5% APY.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CNBC Make It on August 06, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says '" To create things that truly have lasting value, perseverance is a key aspect. #makeit JAMES PARK Fitbit CEO and co-founder'.

node.text:
James Park, the CEO and co-founder of Fitbit, discussed the importance of perseverance when starting a new company. 💪⁠
⁠
At the link in our bio, he shared advice for aspiring entrepreneurs, how Covid has influenced his personal fitness routine and what he considers his greatest failures.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CNBC Make It on August 06, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text:
Your resume is more than a piece of paper — it’s the first impression you make with a potential employer. ⁠
⁠
Grab that notepad! 🗒️ At the link in our bio, we've rounded up 9 action verbs that'll improve your chances of getting noticed. 🙌

node.text: Katie McRose, 26, and her wife Darian travel around Texas to shear sheep, llamas and alpacas. This year, they expect to bring in at least $80,000 servicing over 575 farms. 🐑

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CNBC Make It on August 05, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'The smartest people use a simple model and these 6 phrases to say 'no' when they need to, says CEO-here's how it works 0... 00. #makeit'.

node.text:
Asking for what you want at work is a crucial skill for career growth. But it's just as important to express what you don't want. 🙅‍♂️⁠
⁠
At the link in our bio, we're sharing a step-by-step guide for consciously deciding when to say no (and 6 ways to say it). 📝

node.text:
If you're a millennial looking to live somewhere new, you are most likely considering factors like financial security, job opportunities and quality of life.⁠
⁠
Check out the link in our bio for a list of the top 15 most affordable U.S. states in 2021.

node.accessibility_caption: We’re celebrating Meghan Markle’s 40th birthday with an inspirational quote about knowing your value.

node.text: Happy 40th birthday, Meghan Markle! 🎉 ⁠
